			<div class="p1-4e124504b03-view">
				<div class="p1-4e124504b03-05 p1-4e124504b03-06">
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:24.0722em;top:7.7376em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-07 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="word-spacing:0.0001em;">XPS test file  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:11.9173em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">Purpose: Provide example of this file type  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:14.024em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:-0.0104em;">Document file type: XPS  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:16.1307em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">Version: 1.0  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:18.2373em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;">Remark:  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:22.4507em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">Example content:  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:24.544em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-11" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0009em;">The names "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-13" style="word-spacing:0.0077em;">John Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-14" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0029em;">" for males, "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-15" style="word-spacing:0.0075em;">Jane Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-11" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0008em;">" or "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09">Jane  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:26.664em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-16">Roe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-17" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0029em;">" for females, or "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-16" style="word-spacing:0.0043em;">Jonnie Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-18" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0068em;">" and "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-13" style="word-spacing:0.0076em;">Janie Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">" for  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:28.7707em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-19" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0015em;">children, or just "</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-20">Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-21" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0037em;">" non-gender-specifically are used as  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:30.894em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">placeholder names for a party whose true identity is un-  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:33.0007em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">known or must be withheld in a legal action, case, or dis-  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:35.1073em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">cussion. The names are also used to refer to acorpse or  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:37.214em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-22" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0041em;">hospital patient whose identity is unknown. This practice is  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:39.3207em;z-index:533;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">widely used in the United States and Canada, but is rarely used in other Englis</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-23" style="font-weight:bold;">h</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-24" style="font-weight:bold;">-</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">speaking coun-  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:41.4273em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">tries including the United Kingdom itself, from where the use of "John Doe" in a legal context origi-  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:43.534em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:-0.0052em;">nates. The names Joe Bloggs or John Smith are used in the UK instead, as well as in Australia and  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:45.654em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">New Zealand.  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:49.1607em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">John Doe is sometimes used to refer to a typical male in other contexts as well, in a similar manner  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:50.574em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">to John Q. Public, known in Great Britain as Joe Public, John Smith or Joe Bloggs. For example,  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:51.9762em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">the first name listed on a form is often John Doe, along with a fictional address or other fictional  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:53.3762em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">information to provide an example of how to fill in the form. The name is also used frequently in  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:54.7896em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:-0.0066em;">popular culture, for example in the Frank Capra film </span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-25 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-16" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:-0.0015em;">Meet John Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">. John Doe was also the name  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:56.1895em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">of a 2002 American television series.  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:58.9895em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">Similarly, a child or baby whose identity is unknown may be referred to a</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-26" style="font-weight:bold;">s</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-27" style="word-spacing:0.0084em;">Baby Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">. A notorious  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:60.3895em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">murder case in Kansas City, Missouri, referred to the baby victim a</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-28" style="font-weight:bold;">s</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-12 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-29" style="word-spacing:0.0059em;">Precious Doe</span><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:-0.0013em;">. Other  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:61.8162em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">unidentified female murder victims are Cali Doe and Princess Doe. Additional persons may be  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:63.2162em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">called James Doe, Judy Doe, etc. However, to avoid possible confusion, if two anonymous or  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:64.6295em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-14" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0.0029em;">unknown parties are cited in a specific case or action, the surnames Doe and Roe may be used  </span></div>
					<div class="p1-4e124504b03-01" style="left:6.2933em;top:66.0295em;"><span class="p1-4e124504b03-10 p1-4e124504b03-08 p1-4e124504b03-09" style="font-weight:bold;word-spacing:0em;">simultaneously; for example, "John Doe v. Jane Roe". If several anonymous parties are  </span></div>
